{"tid":1334516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］上訴委員會維持民陣明日集會終點在灣仔","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:05:07.000Z","uid":32323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"468c3cdd773fd9a2b6e563166e98190d4c828fc2","tid":1334516,"uid":32323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:38:24.000Z","msg":"source: rthk<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469383-20190720.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469383-20190720.htm&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=2997dd36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469383-20190720.htm&h=0eb03cc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469383-20190720.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n1030 民陣上訴721遊行安排，上訴委員會成員為：<br />\n彭鍵基博士<br />\n郭永強<br />\n林新強（前香港律師會會長）<br />\n黃浩明（前幫港出聲成員）<br />\n<br />\n同時有香港警察代表"},{"pid":"2c5e3a47b996835885400c13b4349e5ad573ee6b","tid":1334516,"uid":30163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c04f040f4d62c3ec6ba21ee7f943cc7448333bf5","tid":1334516,"uid":224657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"全世界出嚟塞爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422540e02ed87552a9906986e5d744fb35b9f204","tid":1334516,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:39:33.000Z","msg":"到時咁多人, 灣仔一定有人潮管制措施<br />\n人潮可向金鐘,中環及西環<span style=\"color: red;\">散去</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9639a4ec545bf840e28996ed2e069dc47361ec53","tid":1334516,"uid":32323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"1435 【上訴結果】<br />\n<br />\n上訴委員會就民陣上訴作以下裁決：<br />\n－民陣需呼籲參與市民「立即解散」；<br />\n－結束時間由晚上9時改為晚上11時59分；及<br />\n－終點維持於灣仔盧押道。<br />\n<br />\n民陣將嚴格按不反對通知書安排遊行。警方在上訴期間，指遊行人士在到達終點後，可往皇后大道方向，即向南行解散，而不反對通知書中要求民陣安排遊行人士「立即散去」，因此，民陣只能盡力呼籲大家「立即散去」，唯按不反對通知書，民陣沒有責任，亦沒有能力在相關區域安排離開灣仔的交通方法，因此明日散去的交通方法，還請各位當日向安排能力「傑出」、「智力過人」的警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n民陣重申，民陣將盡最大努力，保障遊行路線上參與人士的安全。而任何混亂，還請警方負上全責。"}]}